 Rumple Stiltskin is a critical rationalist who is attitudinally challenged.<br /> <br /> He is well read in the contemporary e-learning literature and has extensive teaching experience. He recently downloaded a <span style="font-style: italic">eXe</span>  copy of Release 0.5. He spent 14 hours developing content for a new  course, and after a power failure, lost everything. He has compiled a  78 page critical review of eXe and has approached you for legal advice  on this incident. What advice do you offer Professor Stiltskin?<div id="view9" style="display:block;"><input type="button" name="btnshow9" value ="Click here" onclick="showAnswer('9',1)"/></div>
