 <div id="s9" class="feedback" style=" display: none;">Apart from recommending a name change, you encourage him to submit his  critical review as a submission to improve the technology. You remind  him of the GPL license and direct him to a copy of the <a href="http://www.firstmonday.org/issues/issue3_3/raymond/">Cathedral and the Bazaar</a>, by Eric Raymond. As an FLOSS advocate, you don't charge for the consultation.</div>
